cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with learning embeddings from visual features, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves representation learning and deep learning techniques (cs.LG), as well as the use of attention mechanisms (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional networks (cs.MM) and the evaluation of the model's performance (cs.NE).
